_sText:
The houses are breakable and the bricks fall down. 

I know there are some bugs:
- Sometimes you stuck in the walls or fallen bricks.
- Sometimes they give you boost if you jump on them.
- Small lighting fails.

THIS MAP WAS ONLY MADE FOR FUN! I DON'T CARE IF YOU HATE, BECAUSE OF THE BUGS!

I think it's pretty fun, especially if you are playing LAN with friends! 

*EDIT: The house might collapse, at the time you spawn. I have only seen this bug after det CSS update 2010. I don't know if it's bugged for everyone, but please comment if you see this bug too.
